literals: 'Diagnostic support allows Milesight to identify issues with your Hotspot in a secure way. Milesight will never have access to private keys and will only ever be able to access your Hotspot and not any other devices on your Network. If you would like to opt-out of diagnostic support please email iot.support@milesight.com from the email used to purchase the Hotspot.'
'Attach the antenna and plug in the provided power adapter.'
'Your Hotspot will boot up, and its Status LED will become Blue when ready.'
'You can find the QR code either directly on your product or on the box you received, and you can also visit the local management-console to get the QR code.'
